{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "$id": "estructurando/spec-parametrico/v0.2",
  "title": "Spec parametrico canonico (entrada de spec_to_ifc.py) — FORWARD-OPEN",
  "$comment": "Contrato C1 'apertura de familias P1' (2026-06-28). FORWARD-OPEN: additionalProperties=true en TODOS los niveles. El cebo (c1-bridge) puede EMITIR POR DELANTE de lo que el compilador autora; lo que C1 aun no entiende se IGNORA, nunca rompe. Esta es la garantia formal de 'sin mas parches': las claves nuevas (huecos en cualquier anfitrion, elementos[].ifcClass de cualquier clase del catalogo bsDD, alineaciones[]) son ADITIVAS y no alteran la semantica de las existentes; los consumidores actuales (estructuras/MEP/lineal/puentes) no regresan.",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ["niveles"],
  "additionalProperties": true,
  "properties": {
    "proyecto": { "type": "string" },
    "esquema": { "type": "string", "enum": ["IFC4", "IFC4X3"], "default": "IFC4",
      "$comment": "IFC4X3 obligatorio si hay alineaciones[] (IfcAlignment no existe en IFC4)." },
    "unidades": { "type": "string", "enum": ["m"], "default": "m" },
    "niveles": {
      "type": "array", "minItems": 1,
      "items": {
        "type": "object", "required": ["nombre", "cota"], "additionalProperties": true,
        "properties": {
          "nombre": { "type": "string" },
          "cota": { "type": "number" }
        }
      }
    },
    "pilares": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "object", "required": ["nombre", "nivel", "pos", "seccion", "altura"],
        "additionalProperties": true,
        "properties": {
          "nombre": { "type": "string" },
          "nivel": { "type": "string" },
          "pos": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "number" }, "minItems": 2, "maxItems": 2 },
          "seccion": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "number", "exclusiveMinimum": 0 }, "minItems": 2, "maxItems": 2 },
          "altura": { "type": "number", "exclusiveMinimum": 0 },
          "material": { "type": "string" }
        }
      }
    },
    "muros": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "object", "required": ["nombre", "nivel", "inicio", "fin", "espesor", "altura"],
        "additionalProperties": true,
        "properties": {
          "nombre": { "type": "string" },
          "nivel": { "type": "string" },
          "inicio": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "number" }, "minItems": 2, "maxItems": 2 },
          "fin": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "number" }, "minItems": 2, "maxItems": 2 },
          "espesor": { "type": "number", "exclusiveMinimum": 0 },
          "altura": { "type": "number", "exclusiveMinimum": 0 },
          "exterior": { "type": "boolean" },
          "material": { "type": "string" },
          "huecos": {
            "type": "array",
            "$comment": "HUECOS GENERALIZADOS (via unica). En muro: ancho x alto situados por 'pos' a lo largo del muro + 'alfeizar'. Opcional 'tipo':'puerta'|'ventana' rellena el hueco (IfcDoor/IfcWindow).",
            "items": {
              "type": "object", "required": ["ancho", "alto", "pos"], "additionalProperties": true,
              "properties": {
                "ancho": { "type": "number", "exclusiveMinimum": 0 },
                "alto": { "type": "number", "exclusiveMinimum": 0 },
                "pos": { "type": "number" },
                "alfeizar": { "type": "number" },
                "tipo": { "type": "string", "enum": ["puerta", "ventana"] }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "losas": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "object", "required": ["nombre", "nivel", "contorno", "espesor"],
        "additionalProperties": true,
        "properties": {
          "nombre": { "type": "string" },
          "nivel": { "type": "string" },
          "contorno": {
            "type": "array", "minItems": 3,
            "items": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "number" }, "minItems": 2, "maxItems": 2 }
          },
          "espesor": { "type": "number", "exclusiveMinimum": 0 },
          "material": { "type": "string" },
          "tipo": { "type": "string", "enum": ["macizo", "nervado", "reticular", "unidireccional"] },
          "huecos": {
            "type": "array",
            "$comment": "HUECOS GENERALIZADOS en anfitrion HORIZONTAL (losa/cubierta): prisma vertical que atraviesa el canto. Rectangular por 'pos':[x,y]+ancho+largo, o poligonal por 'contorno':[[x,y],...].",
            "items": {
              "type": "object", "additionalProperties": true,
              "properties": {
                "pos": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "number" }, "minItems": 2, "maxItems": 2 },
                "ancho": { "type": "number", "exclusiveMinimum": 0 },
                "largo": { "type": "number", "exclusiveMinimum": 0 },
                "contorno": {
                  "type": "array", "minItems": 3,
                  "items": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "number" }, "minItems": 2, "maxItems": 2 }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "elementos": {
      "type": "array",
      "$comment": "CATALOGO DE CLASES ABIERTO: 'ifcClass' (alias historico 'clase') autora CUALQUIER IfcClass concreta del catalogo bsDD del esquema (p.ej. IfcTransportElement=ascensor) SIN lista cerrada — las clases futuras entran sin re-bump del contrato.",
      "items": {
        "type": "object", "additionalProperties": true,
        "properties": {
          "ifcClass": { "type": "string" },
          "clase": { "type": "string" },
          "nombre": { "type": "string" },
          "nivel": { "type": "string" },
          "pos": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "number" }, "minItems": 2, "maxItems": 2 },
          "cota": { "type": "number" },
          "predefined": { "type": "string" },
          "material": { "type": "string" },
          "huecos": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "object", "additionalProperties": true } }
        }
      }
    },
    "alineaciones": {
      "type": "array",
      "$comment": "ALINEACIONES COMPLETAS -> IfcAlignment (reutiliza la maquinaria de la Ola 5; legible por ifc_to_model_lineal.py). planta: recta/clotoide/curva; alzado: rasantes/acuerdos; peralte; georref. Requiere esquema IFC4X3.",
      "items": {
        "type": "object", "required": ["planta"], "additionalProperties": true,
        "properties": {
          "nombre": { "type": "string" },
          "infraestructura": { "type": "object", "additionalProperties": true,
            "properties": { "clase": { "type": "string" }, "nombre": { "type": "string" } } },
          "ancho_ref": { "type": "number", "exclusiveMinimum": 0 },
          "inicio": { "type": "object", "additionalProperties": true,
            "properties": { "x": {"type":"number"}, "y": {"type":"number"},
              "acimut_deg": {"type":"number"}, "acimut_rad": {"type":"number"}, "cota": {"type":"number"} } },
          "planta": {
            "type": "array", "minItems": 1,
            "items": { "type": "object", "required": ["tipo", "longitud"], "additionalProperties": true,
              "properties": {
                "tipo": { "type": "string", "$comment": "recta|clotoide|curva (o LINE/CLOTHOID/CIRCULARARC)" },
                "longitud": { "type": "number", "exclusiveMinimum": 0 },
                "radio": { "type": "number" }, "radio_ini": { "type": "number" }, "radio_fin": { "type": "number" }
              } }
          },
          "alzado": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": { "type": "object", "required": ["tipo", "longitud"], "additionalProperties": true,
              "properties": {
                "tipo": { "type": "string", "$comment": "rampa|acuerdo (o CONSTANTGRADIENT/PARABOLICARC)" },
                "longitud": { "type": "number", "exclusiveMinimum": 0 },
                "pendiente_ini": { "type": "number" }, "pendiente_fin": { "type": "number" },
                "kv": { "type": "number" }
              } }
          },
          "peralte": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": { "type": "object", "additionalProperties": true,
              "properties": {
                "tipo": { "type": "string", "$comment": "constante|transicion (o CONSTANTCANT/LINEARTRANSITION)" },
                "longitud": { "type": "number" },
                "peralte_ini_pct": { "type": "number" }, "peralte_fin_pct": { "type": "number" }
              } }
          },
          "georref": { "type": "object", "additionalProperties": true,
            "properties": {
              "epsg": { "type": "string" }, "descripcion": { "type": "string" },
              "datum_geodesico": { "type": "string" }, "datum_vertical": { "type": "string" },
              "map_projection": { "type": "string" }, "map_zone": { "type": "string" },
              "origen_e": { "type": "number" }, "origen_n": { "type": "number" }, "altura": { "type": "number" },
              "rotacion_deg": { "type": "number" }, "rotacion_rad": { "type": "number" }, "escala": { "type": "number" }
            } }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
